      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEW ARRANGEMENT (3) showed strong early pace from the wide draw and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing sixth over 300m this track in 17.21. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Looks the one to beat on his best form. THAI BUTTERFLY (6) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (17.12). Can figure in the finish. BUSTER BOURBSKI (2) was well fancied last time on the strength of the win two back but could only manage second (17.05) at this track. Will give a great sight again. SNAG (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
